thread.title: BRIEF-Soft Computing Q3 revenue rises 4 pct to 9.1 million euros
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Soft Computing Q3 revenue rises 4 pct to 9.1 million euros | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Soft Computing Q3 revenue rises 4 pct to 9.1 million euros
text:
Oct 22 Soft Computing SA :
* Reports Q3 revenue of 9.1 million euros ($10.13 million) compared to 8.7 million euros a year ago
* Says growth should continue in coming months Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8984 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
